{"tid":1693680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"放棄感化藍色老豆？不，我要比佢更紅更黑","createTime":"2019-11-04T17:42:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T01:08:52.000Z","uid":322470,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f7e462ecc482d0f13d89432f3a54055eb4f137d8","tid":1693680,"uid":322470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:42:41.000Z","msg":"（我並不持有我老豆，所以唔存在可以放棄老豆呢件事；我有感化我老豆嘅權利，而我仲未諗住放棄。）<br />\n<br />\n老豆背景：已退休、住開大灣區，有樓收租。<br />\n                   平時最鍾意用we7同同鄉吹水，有次仲<br />\n                   想幫同鄉會拎晒我地全屋身份證申請損<br />\n                   民。覺得中國最勁最團結唔會侵略人<br />\n                   地，美國會冧會倒台係遲早嘅事。<br />\n                   屌林鄭廢，警察都係打份工，不過<br />\n                   見到手足俾人打都係會拍手讚好。<br />\n                   <br />\n<br />\n事源就係今日老豆又咁啱落咗黎，我返到屋企第一下就即刻聽到佢睇電視講到科大位手足墮樓單野。因為我深知我老豆係果種傳統大男人，乜都只有自己啱，人地錯（同某啲object雷同實屬巧合），所以我決定要比佢更紅更黑，去將佢地嘅想法演繹到極致。<br />\n<br />\n我當堂附和，然後話：「係呀抵撚死呀，啱呀爽快呀，睇多幾次吖。」跟手搶遙控、轉開Apple TV，準備loop幫港出聲，睇果啲所謂「暴徒」俾人打嘅片然後要同佢一齊睇，睇一次講一次抵死。點知佢話：「我唔睇呢啲㗎，唔係直播剪接過，假嘅。」呵，原來都知嘅，我就話：「理得佢真定假吖，最緊要睇得爽吖嘛，黎吖睇吖」佢就話：「我尋晚睇咗直播喇。」我回：「唔係吖，睇下開心吓好呀。」如是者來來回回，佢就改第句：「果啲仆街黎㗎，你明唔明呀？」「係呀仆街黎㗎，唔死無撚用呀，最好全部死撚晒佢。」佢一面狐疑，硬就不信：「你都扮嘅。」我反串一下：「你理得我真定假，我同你企同一立場一齊屌一齊鬧。」<br />\n<br />\n係呢度我驚老豆糖尿附帶嘅血壓飆升，稍為放鬆一下，轉返下台，返到電視節目，然後我突然黎個回馬槍，屌電視節目入面果個係仆街，最好仆街死（多有冒犯，請見諒），我老豆轉台，明珠台，「屌你買西片俾外國賺錢做咩！？」；Viu，「播個人帶口罩做乜撚！？」；香港開電視，「立法會果班全部都仆街黎㗎！」佢轉一下我屌一下，佢終於忍唔住：「你咁激動做咩，果啲假㗎剪出黎㗎。」我揸緊拳頭，唧盡所有力氣：「香港家陣乜都假嘅，我點樣生活呀？我真係唔知點生活呀。」<br />\n<br />\n語畢，我撳個央視唔知乜柒台俾佢，然後我剝衫行開一邊做push up。我老豆之後無再講啲咩，係叫我幫佢搞手機野。我都無托佢手踭，好聲好氣幫佢。<br />\n跟住就全屋靜咗。<br />\n<br />\n首先我想對我假膠屌咗嘅人衷心致歉，尤其係科大周同學，你要撐住。<br />\n<br />\n我要演，演一個藍極，紅極，黑嘅極致出黎，俾佢睇呢啲思想幾咁涼薄醜惡。我都唔係想自命清高講咩大道理，但我只係想講俾佢地聽，一個後生仔要生活係宜家呢個香港係幾咁痛苦，我亦唔想聽佢貪一時口癮（係我面前）羞辱賭上自己未來嘅香港人。唔知呢段小小嘅假膠有幾大作用，但之後我都會繼續反客為主，演佢地最撚鍾意嘅「小&middot;粉&middot;紅～」<br />\n<br />\n利申：愛老豆，愛香港，愛香港人（只限真果啲）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23bf1b6de43653c363878c2e554b4fc4060190b","tid":1693680,"uid":34217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:48:58.000Z","msg":"呢句真, 紅撚過佢, 等佢反思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870a1fe374f6538863c3a7e75ebd12571c8d4516","tid":1693680,"uid":332036,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:50:29.000Z","msg":"支持手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係咁成功感化左老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好放棄"},{"pid":"d914b5835220d5cbbd4729a624c5aba9479bc4bf","tid":1693680,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:53:08.000Z","msg":"我細佬本身淺黃 都係用類似方法陪老豆 點知佢自己睇得太多變咗深藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4379f3de6d0c63a6e47bcc740fa9c4864c94baa8","tid":1693680,"uid":154470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d914b5835220d5cbbd4729a624c5aba9479bc4bf","tid":1693680,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:53:08.000Z","msg":"我細佬本身淺黃 都係用類似方法陪老豆 點知佢自己睇得太多變咗深藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:56:40.000Z","msg":"點算"},{"pid":"0d4e3e06bb462a8fb051abe12a2c057eb7e810f2","tid":1693680,"uid":271248,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d914b5835220d5cbbd4729a624c5aba9479bc4bf","tid":1693680,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:53:08.000Z","msg":"我細佬本身淺黃 都係用類似方法陪老豆 點知佢自己睇得太多變咗深藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:58:32.000Z","msg":"其實淺黃本身就係藍<br />\n佢地之所以係淺黃<br />\n係因為身邊嘅人黃囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfdf10ef5bab787a22d7475b856cee995b68a07","tid":1693680,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4379f3de6d0c63a6e47bcc740fa9c4864c94baa8","tid":1693680,"uid":154470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d914b5835220d5cbbd4729a624c5aba9479bc4bf","tid":1693680,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:53:08.000Z","msg":"我細佬本身淺黃 都係用類似方法陪老豆 點知佢自己睇得太多變咗深藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:56:40.000Z","msg":"點算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:01:09.000Z","msg":"無咗計傾喇同佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb2f0857e3c061d36ab29faca9eca16b1a0b0bc","tid":1693680,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d914b5835220d5cbbd4729a624c5aba9479bc4bf","tid":1693680,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:53:08.000Z","msg":"我細佬本身淺黃 都係用類似方法陪老豆 點知佢自己睇得太多變咗深藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:09:22.000Z","msg":"戇居仔喊出黎"},{"pid":"b9118229eece2448a4d272ea6b1261858729a60c","tid":1693680,"uid":300642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:12:16.000Z","msg":"我早兩日都想用呢招，但唸唸下都係唔想係我屋企人身上曬時間<br />\n<br />\n巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0a2554a168c559c0fe3f75fb2a8f45a2e1e33e","tid":1693680,"uid":178800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T18:27:57.000Z","msg":"真正深藍根本無咁易比你感化<br />\n好似今日藍屍同事講番太古斬人單野<br />\n又話班黑衣人撩交打先<br />\n又話伸縮警棍唔岩<br />\n<br />\n完全無視被斬傷者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後又話條友check到精神病<br />\n監都唔洗坐"},{"pid":"c48fa14325c8aa01048d80f5aff608160869b029","tid":1693680,"uid":1818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T20:04:37.000Z","msg":"on撚9<br />\n我阿婆藍撚到紅果隻<br />\n佢一講話啲手足搞事<br />\n我就改左wifi密碼<br />\n之後佢聲都唔敢再聲"},{"pid":"db07b98190d316907a2c9ecae3655bc64ef6f762","tid":1693680,"uid":127328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T20:17:56.000Z","msg":"用極左路線，慢慢顯出鬥死你老豆既心，佢就會驚，轉做中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6273460c92b55b9ecd404bda239d09830748b446","tid":1693680,"uid":258571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d914b5835220d5cbbd4729a624c5aba9479bc4bf","tid":1693680,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:53:08.000Z","msg":"我細佬本身淺黃 都係用類似方法陪老豆 點知佢自己睇得太多變咗深藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T20:27:10.000Z","msg":"走火入魔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451cfc03514e33203bde182ba9cf411fe313c5ec","tid":1693680,"uid":22971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d914b5835220d5cbbd4729a624c5aba9479bc4bf","tid":1693680,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:53:08.000Z","msg":"我細佬本身淺黃 都係用類似方法陪老豆 點知佢自己睇得太多變咗深藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T20:45:49.000Z","msg":"真定假<br />\n講多少少嚟聽吓"},{"pid":"62ce9ace9dc5e0a970f68e24ea7d202e0dfe412a","tid":1693680,"uid":211293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d4e3e06bb462a8fb051abe12a2c057eb7e810f2","tid":1693680,"uid":271248,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d914b5835220d5cbbd4729a624c5aba9479bc4bf","tid":1693680,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:53:08.000Z","msg":"我細佬本身淺黃 都係用類似方法陪老豆 點知佢自己睇得太多變咗深藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:58:32.000Z","msg":"其實淺黃本身就係藍<br />\n佢地之所以係淺黃<br />\n係因為身邊嘅人黃囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T20:51:44.000Z","msg":"嗰啲其實就當係跟潮流咁<br />\n人哋著潮牌 你唔著 你好柒<br />\n人哋屌政府 你唔屌 你好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗唔柒我梗係話自己係黃啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1258c14999bda94fde0444901b51cd22866c5af2","tid":1693680,"uid":118455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T21:08:35.000Z","msg":"對付藍絲父母 其實唯一出路都係搬出去 一世唔見唔撚洗眼怨 再遲下樓主你會發現溝通唔到 佢地個腦生草"},{"pid":"393d6629020118f657b0c141dbd61f2c906e00dc","tid":1693680,"uid":322470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1258c14999bda94fde0444901b51cd22866c5af2","tid":1693680,"uid":118455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T21:08:35.000Z","msg":"對付藍絲父母 其實唯一出路都係搬出去 一世唔見唔撚洗眼怨 再遲下樓主你會發現溝通唔到 佢地個腦生草"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T00:13:10.000Z","msg":"其實佢平時對人對物都咁king of 臭口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，完全唔識安慰人。不過本質都上好錫我地，所以無隔夜仇嘅。<br />\n<br />\n同埋呢幾個月都試過幾過幾種玩法：<br />\n1.佢行埋黎俾we7 d乜野示威者收錢價碼錄音我聽，我聽完之後淨係笑，唔出聲，之後佢都無癮敗走。<br />\n<br />\n2. 反串佢，佢話咩示威者吸毒所以暴力升級，正黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我話係囉仆街，啲POPO又唔日日捉新beyond果啲，同埋有冇做好啲中國毒品留入管理控呀？之後佢無聲出。<br />\n<br />\n3. 一睇直播我自己入房睇唔同佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時其他野我都會問候我老豆身體狀況，我老豆都年事高又多病痛，我都唔係想佢覺醒啲乜，只係想佢臨老都帶住呢類思想。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6b91b83d8fd78d3825e7e19ed097d313128da5","tid":1693680,"uid":271248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62ce9ace9dc5e0a970f68e24ea7d202e0dfe412a","tid":1693680,"uid":211293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d4e3e06bb462a8fb051abe12a2c057eb7e810f2","tid":1693680,"uid":271248,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d914b5835220d5cbbd4729a624c5aba9479bc4bf","tid":1693680,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:53:08.000Z","msg":"我細佬本身淺黃 都係用類似方法陪老豆 點知佢自己睇得太多變咗深藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:58:32.000Z","msg":"其實淺黃本身就係藍<br />\n佢地之所以係淺黃<br />\n係因為身邊嘅人黃囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T20:51:44.000Z","msg"